What you need to know:

Prior to his death, Odera was paralysed on one side of the body and had lost his vision. He underwent his first surgery in 2009 before the second one was conducted early this year.Odera, who hailed from Nyahera in Kisumu County, has left behind three children (Weber Otieno,Nyerere Oduor and Joshua Odhiambo) and wife, Mophine.Â 